 Boom Leeds 筹集了 1.5 万英镑（其中 4.5 万英镑是维持营业所需的资金） https://www.nme.com/news/music/boom-leeds-raises-15k-of-45k-needed-to-keep-open-3580020?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=boom-leeds-raises-15k-保持开放需要 45kTom Skinner Wed, 31 Jan 2024 16:59:47 +0000 Music NewsNewsNME RadarHardcoreMetalPunk https://www.nme.com/?p=3580020 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>草根会场的一份声明解释说：“未来肯定是更加光明的，但它仍然充满挑战和不确定性。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/boom-leeds-raises-15k-of-45k-needed-to-keep-open-3580020">《Boom Leeds》筹集了 1.5 万英镑，维持营业所需的 4.5 万英镑</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Boom Leeds 是一家致力于朋克、硬核和金属音乐的草根场所，已从慈善演出中筹集了 15,000 英镑，这使其免于永久关闭。</p><p>早在 11 月，这个可容纳 250 人的空间就发布了一份<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CzdihxWiHGp/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">声明</a>，解释了其所面临的充满挑战的财务状况。该消息引用了“与<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/coronavirus">新冠病毒</a>相关的巨额债务”以及持续的生活成本危机的影响。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/boom-leeds-venue-closing-save-our-home-benefit-show-radar-3565053">繁荣利兹：为什么英国硬核场景正在努力拯救重要的草根场地</a></strong></li></ul><p>“不幸的是，Boom 在压力下苦苦挣扎，”它继续说道。</p><p>声明随后强调了<a href="https://www.musicvenuetrust.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">音乐场所信托基金会</a>（MVT）最近的一份报告，该报告显示125个英国基层场地在2023年关闭（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/2023-was-worst-year-for-venue-closures-while-no-one-in-music-industry-seems-to-care-say-mvt-3562266">如MVT告诉<em>NME</em> ，“最糟糕的一年”是“最糟糕的一年”</a> ）。</p><p> Boom Leeds继续宣布一系列的福利节目和“筹款计划”，以确保其未来。现在，老板说他们已经筹集了45,000英镑的目标数字中的15,000英镑。</p><p> “本月，我们还清了一大笔严重的债务，这些债务威胁到即将关闭场地，”该邮报继续说道。</p><p> “没有筹款活动，今天我们将写一份声明，以解释繁荣即将结束。”</p><p>它补充说：“我们要感谢厌恶，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/static-dress">静态着装</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/higher-power">更高的力量</a>，轻轻地杀死我，很少爱，鲜血，身体网络，水星，永恒的休息，flex，害虫控制，大锅，脱离，脱离接触，不受惩罚和蒲公英，贡献筹款。</p><p> “我们还要感谢所有粉丝，客户和我们的朋友的支持。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C2vDkY6i2lf/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-